## Conversation Backup Workflow

Before clearing conversation history (to free up context), backup your inputs:

```bash
# 1. Export all your inputs to markdown
/export-inputs

# 2. The backup is saved to notes/user_inputs_backup_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.md

# 3. Now safe to clear conversations
```

This preserves your feature requests, decisions, and debugging sessions for future reference.
